data.description: This quaint craftsman style , 3 BR/2 BTH cottage home, with it's open concept floor plan, allows for easy entertaining with family and friends.  The great room features 11 ft ceilings with exposed beams and a gas fireplace.  The kitchen boasts granite countertops and bar area for additional seating.  In the dining area, you will find craftsman wainscoting and leads you to the outdoor covered porch patio area with fenced in backyard.   Located close to downtown, beaches and much more.  We invite you to view this home today!
